description: Associates a list of analytics datasets for a given Amazon Connect instance to a target account. You can associate multiple datasets in a single call.

parameters.name: InstanceId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Connect instance. You can find the instance ID in the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the instance.

parameters.name: DataSetIds
parameters.description: An array of dataset identifiers to associate. (string) ---

nested_items.name: Created
nested_items.description: Information about associations that are successfully created: DataSetId, TargetAccountId, ResourceShareId, ResourceShareArn.

nested_items.name: TargetAccountId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the target account.

nested_items.name: ResourceShareId
nested_items.description: The Resource Access Manager share ID.

nested_items.name: ResourceShareArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Resource Access Manager share.

nested_items.name: ResourceShareStatus
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services Resource Access Manager status of association.

nested_items.name: Errors
nested_items.description: A list of errors for datasets that aren't successfully associated with the target account.

nested_items.name: ErrorMessage
nested_items.description: The corresponding error message for the error code.
